.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765bebbad5a1525286958aadef0b8015e247090b","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4同5係邊個咁教你？</blockquote>睇輝sir YouTube</blockquote>一轉二鬆極力子架車都會照行，慢慢鬆咗先再慢慢扭油<br />\n你鬆極力子前就畀空油，如果你鬆<span class=\"red\">得</span>快架車會標前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f9aef469d71a08a540e3532c7f7d2c1a33d88021","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"同埋你都係上完第一堂姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上多幾堂先啦"},{"pid":"e5f400fa44878069176c15beffd6278064aad622","tid":2450610,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"油門平時可以點練，一係好大油，一係收曬油，<br />\n唔識keep住定速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"雙手放鬆，手掙下垂，唔使死力握油門<br />\n咁先可以靈活控制油門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8837ecaad286bee2f1b036717bbf1e4064ae9f","tid":2450610,"uid":190818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b7e9ac97501e38997b63a9592b11aa5899c7c8f3","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"上完第1堂強制, 發覺手腳完全唔協調<br />\n有無咩口訣可以記下?<br />\n例如轉波:<br />\n1. 收油<br />\n2. 按極力子<br />\n3. 轉波<br />\n4. 俾油<br />\n5. 鬆極力子<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他? 幾時用前迫力, 幾時用後迫力呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"4, 5 係同時做"},{"pid":"180399590b015be13e505ff8274a70c3ad7b36ca","tid":2450610,"uid":190818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":3