01e8745a","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"一波起步, 油門去到幾千轉先開車?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"望轉數錶就輸咗啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"咁點好?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:24:12.000Z","msg":"憑感覺<br />\n<br />\n你考老強咋 唔係斜路起步 左手慢放 感受吓個磨擦點  到咗磨擦點 就定住油 但係記住記住記住 左手都係keep住未放 行一兩個車位先慢慢放晒"},{"pid":"93ba7feca05477c71978d1a73568dde39b3d483f","tid":2450610,"uid":190818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c039935b175242ec8f508909ea1a1be201e8745a","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"一波起步, 油門去到幾千轉先開車?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:24:18.000Z","msg":"平時部車無轉數錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔識答你<br />\n通常開少少油門，聽到唔係空轉都夠起步<br />\n熟咗手可以唔駛提前俾定油"},{"pid":"c9d8ed5fb8c5ecb9e95417c1f43a591219159186","tid":2450610,"uid":116696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c039935b175242ec8f508909ea1a1be201e8745a","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"一波起步, 油門去到幾千轉先開車?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"我下個月考老強<br />\n起步比大油 聽到好嘈engine聲 ~3000轉咁上下<br />\n慢放極力子同時輕輕比油 <br />\n入第一個彎前轉2波 收油拉極力子剔上2波<br />\n即放極力子 個人傾側順住轉 覺得太快就踩一踩腳制<br />\n基本上一定要補鐘自己練 練多幾個鐘就熟"},{"pid":"17507dad5ec31d154dffe39a2c34ea0fdf85a839","tid":2450610,"uid":116824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"油門平時可以點練，一係好大油，一係收曬油，<br />\n唔識keep住定速"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:34:32.000Z","msg":"我都係咁"},{"pid":"bbba6633b04ce533b67b03793b92aa6c1d9eed29","tid":2450610,"uid":201197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"油門平時可以點練，一係好大油，一係收曬油，<br />\n唔識keep住定速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"基本上油門先係電單車最重要嘅一還<br />\n其次係視野同極力子, 頭尾掣唔好拿死就得架喇(要自己感受下,先腳制後手制)<br />\n控油一開始試下劍指, 熟習咗用虎口鍊少少就收返兩隻手只落黎, 我頭既年揸車有時都會照用劍指<br />\n初學者要被逼開得慢, 低波行駛, 所以扭少少都好彈<br />\n練熟啲起步放極力子嘅速度, 放嘅速度秘訣係先快後晚, <br />\n熟咗之後啖油就會越黎越大, 就會越黎越順<br />\n<br />\n練得多就得, 真係工多藝熟"},{"pid":"48b294d001a6d0ee547d4b7a9a9c0d8822d378be","tid":2450610,"uid":201197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:39:31.000Z","msg":"理論上<br />\n123 係同時做<br />\n45 係同時做 (不過5 係先快後慢)"},{"pid":"10d2fecd0d5c9966143a4781ec86e1019e287965","tid":2450610,"uid":201197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"油門平時可以點練，一係好大油，一係收曬油，<br />\n唔識keep住定速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-x8pxX1yHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU-x8pxX1yHQ&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=f652f43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U-x8pxX1yHQ</a><br />\n<br />\n睇3:50"},{"pid":"06049638a7a2d29d815368543f31743eab75ae51","tid":2450610,"uid":48901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:42:32.000Z","msg":"應該係<br />\n收油<br />\n快乸極力子<br />\n轉波<br />\n鬆極力子<br />\n補油<br />\n<br />\n如果比完油再鬆極力子有機會撩尾"},{"pid":"40e8ae3c2aed1e5e318c65b5a28b282927b5a522","tid":2450610,"uid":201197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5fd621ff73f695b8101c87d3f06b7d44226e95","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"油門平時可以點練，一係好大油，一係收曬油，<br />\n唔識keep住定速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"<