fcda1","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"尾brake係拖慢架車，臨停定前先配合埋頭brake將架車完全收停。但要控制好個力度，好多人驚停唔切就會大力揸頭brake，份頭一中就好易失平衡落腳。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"即係唔好咁大力揸頭break? <br />\n成日停個陣車Chok 得太勁 落咗右"},{"pid":"3be5034cb5aa5f4fe339dcc27513c8233ae32311","tid":2450610,"uid":157727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9dc08b0a547b7843e2765d667d6399b887d25d","tid":2450610,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"轉波係收油，快收極力子，剔二波。慢放極力子，先再比油<br />\n比住油放極力子會變火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"其實想問 如果俾油開車 再即時轉2波 會唔會好易死火<br />\n利申 路強"},{"pid":"fc05f435de9fb20b255861782e63edbbbda06f88","tid":2450610,"uid":157727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0748a34a79ef6d915bed64a58b9ead42cc0fde7d","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f0857a4f89bfe5939128f7f84a7d1973679ff5","tid":2450610,"uid":337723,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"25bfbdf00c44d1c7de0832a387cd8ff66cf590ef","tid":2450610,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"4同5係邊個咁教你？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:06:28.000Z","msg":"睇輝sir YouTube"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:10:13.000Z","msg":"一轉二鬆極力子架車都會照行，慢慢鬆咗先再慢慢扭油<br />\n你鬆極力子前就畀空油，如果你鬆定快架車會標前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:27:37.000Z","msg":"但好驚一轉二 唔夠油會死火"},{"pid":"23e0351de490e3775c63402169e0b0a81eab1e9d","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c17fae3d69fbb13ff63741f3c44039680c43c335","tid":2450610,"uid":157727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee39d81e3a09282632d3bd695ea7f2cb70ffcda1","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:06:46.000Z","msg":"尾brake係拖慢架車，臨停定前先配合埋頭brake將架車完全收停。但要控制好個力度，好多人驚停唔切就會大力揸頭brake，份頭一中就好易失平衡落腳。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"即係唔好咁大力揸頭break? <br />\n成日停個陣車Chok 得太勁 落咗右"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"你個情況就係頭brake太勁，一停嗰下會鐘頭，一鐘就好易失平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我學時師傅講，尾brake係拖慢架車，慢到差唔多到停車位置先落埋頭brake。咁就唔會因為覺得架車過快，你依賴晒頭brake而搞到鐘頭。"},{"pid":"b4395bae7a73d7aa45dc516387f5b2aba4bb6069","tid":2450610,"uid":122885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3be5034cb5aa5f4fe339dcc27513c8233ae32311","tid":2450610,"uid":157727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a9dc08b0a547b7843e2765d667d6399b887d25d","tid":2450610,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:08:34.000Z","msg":"轉波係收油，快收極力子，剔二波。慢放極力子，先再比油<br />\n比住油放極力子會變火箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"其實想問 如果俾油開車 再即時轉2波 會唔會好易死火<br />\n利申 路強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"除非你好熟油門控制，轉完二波架車打冷震想死火時，你扭好深油去吊返起轉數，如果唔係我相信8-9成都死火<br />\n<br />\n一波起步，行到架車引擎開始嘈就轉二波會穩陣啲"}]}